ra'' | [[British NVC community MG2|MG2]], [[British NVC community MG3|MG3]], [[British NVC community MG4|MG4]], [[British NVC community MG5|MG5]], [[British NVC community MG6|MG6]], [[British NVC community MG8|MG8]], [[British NVC community MG11|MG11]], [[British NVC community MG12|MG12]], [[British NVC community MC1|MC1]], [[British NVC community MC2|MC2]], [[British NVC community MC3|MC3]], [[British NVC community MC4|MC4]], [[British NVC community MC5|MC5]], [[British NVC community MC6|MC6]], [[British NVC community MC10|MC10]], [[British NVC community CG6|CG6]], [[British NVC community CG10|CG10]], [[British NVC community SD19|SD19]], [[British NVC community MC12|MC12]] |- | [[Viviparous fescue]] | ''Festuca vivipara'' | [[British NVC community H20|H20]] |- | [[Yorkshire-fog]] | ''Holcus lanatus'' | [[British NVC community MG3|MG3]], [[British NVC community MG4|MG4]], [[British NVC community MG5|MG5]], [[British NVC community MG6|MG6]], [[British NVC community MG8|MG8]], [[British NVC community MG9|MG9]], [[British NVC community MG10|MG10]], [[British NVC community H7|H7]], [[British NVC community MC12|MC12]] |- | [[Creeping soft-grass]] | ''Holcus mollis'' | [[British NVC community W11|W11]] |- | [[Crested hair-grass]] | ''Koeleria macrantha'' | [[British NVC community CG2|CG2]] |- | [[Perennial rye-grass]] | ''Lolium perenne'' | [[British NVC community MG4|MG4]], [[British NVC community MG6|MG6]] |- | [[Purple moor-grass]] | ''Molinia caerulea'' | [[British NVC community H3|H3]], [[British NVC community H4|H4]], [[British NVC community H5|H5]] |- | [[Common reed]] | ''Phragmites australis'' | [[British NVC community W2|W2]] |- | [[Annual meadow-grass]] | ''Poa annua'' | [[British NVC community OV4|OV4]], [[British NVC community OV5|OV5]], [[British NVC community OV20|OV20]] |- | [[Smooth meadow-grass]] | ''Poa pratensis'' | [[British NVC community SD12|SD12]] |- | [[British NVC community MG3|MG3]], [[rough meadow-grass]] | ''Poa trivialis'' | [[British NVC com