{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2017}} {{Use British English|date=October 2017}} The '''Regius Professor of Natural History''' is a [[Regius Professor]]ship at the [[University of Aberdeen]] in Scotland. It was originally called the Regius Professor of Civil and Natural History at [[Marischal College]] until in 1860 [[Marischal College]] and [[King's College, Aberdeen|King's College]]s merged to form the University of Aberdeen, and the title changed to Natural History.
